@startuml SC-29-Dashboard-Consultant
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Consulter Dashboard (Consultant)

object Consultant
object "Dashboard Interface" as DashboardUI
object "Service Analytics" as ServiceAnalytics
object "Service Clients" as ServiceClients
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit

Consultant --> DashboardUI : 1: acceder("Dashboard")
DashboardUI --> ServiceAnalytics : 2: obtenirDonneesDashboard(consultantId)
ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceClients : 3: obtenirMesClients(consultantId)
ServiceClients --> BaseDonnees : 4: executerRequete(clients)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceClients : 4.1: listeClients[]
ServiceClients --> ServiceAnalytics : 5: donneeClient
ServiceAnalytics --> BaseDonnees : 6: executerRequete(statistiques)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceAnalytics : 6.1: stats

ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceAudit : 6.2: enregistrerAction("DASHBOARD_CONSULTE")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 6.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceAnalytics --> DashboardUI : 7: donneesDashboard
DashboardUI --> Consultant : 8: afficher(dashboard)

note right of ServiceAnalytics
Metriques affichees:
- Nombre clients
- Employes geres
- Fiches paie generees
- Alertes en attente
- Dernieres actions
end note

@enduml
